  "original_title": "\u0db4\u0dd9\u0db8\u0dca\u0dc0\u0dad\u0dd2\u0dba\u0d9c\u0dda \u0dc4\u0ddc\u0dbb \u0d85\u0dbd\u0dca\u0dbd\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1 \u0d85\u0db6\u0dcf\u0dba \u0d87\u0db1\u0dca\u0daf \u0dad\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0dab\u0dba\u0dcf \u0db8\u0dcf\u0da7\u0dca\u0da7\u0dd4",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The young man who wore a robe to catch his girlfriend was caught",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A young Muslim man who was wearing an abaya dress worn by Muslim women and a burqa was taken into custody by the security officers of the Galle railway station and handed over to the Galle police this morning (19).",
        "A 27-year-old Muslim youth from Galle Makuluwa has been arrested.",
        "He arrived at the railway station this morning and bought a ticket to Colombo and the security officers who were suspicious of his voice checked him.",
        "There, the railway security officers saw that he was a man, even though he was wearing a Muslim woman's dress.",
        "Later, the railway security officers handed him over to the police and during the questioning by the police, he said that according to information received that his girlfriend was having a relationship with another young man and that they were coming to Galle railway station, he came dressed in a woman's dress.",
        "According to the instructions of Mr. C.I.Kodithuvakku, the station commander of the security department of the Galle railway station, the sergeants M.D.S.T.Abeyratne and S.J.Kalengsuriya W.H.Ariyaratne caught the suspect and handed him over to the police."
      ],
